Want to learn about the [MeshJS](https://meshjs.dev/) library? Join our weekly Live Coding sessions on this versatile Cardano library.

*Mesh Live Coding* aims to help people try out new things and learn. Everyone is welcome to join and explore something new.

Invite link at: <https://gimbalabs.com/calendar>

Best,

Sebastian Pabon
